metadata.name: Harmony in Simplicity
metadata.description: The artwork portrays the beauty of the Japanese aesthetic, with clean lines and natural materials creating a sense of harmony between the interior and exterior spaces. The piece  invites the viewer to appreciate the simplicity and elegance of the design, which emphasizes functionality and connection to nature. It showcases the artistry of Japanese architecture and design, and evokes a sense of tranquility and peacefulness that is associated with the traditional Japanese way of life.
